headline.sub: Rocket fired from Syria kills 7 in Lebanese border town
headline.main: Rocket fired from Syria kills 7 in Lebanese border town

docs.snippet: Rocket fire into a Lebanese border town killed at least seven people, in one of several such salvoes to hit towns bordering war-torn Syria. Deborah Lutterbeck reports....
docs.lead_paragraph: Rocket fire into a Lebanese border town killed at least seven people, in one of several such salvoes to hit towns bordering war-torn Syria. Deborah Lutterbeck reports.

headline.print_headline: Figure Skating: Russia's Lipnitskaia Beats Favorites to Win Gold
headline.main: Figure Skating: Russia's Lipnitskaia Beats Favorites to Win Gold

docs.snippet: Julia Lipnitskaia's youthful exuberance shone out as the 15-year-old Russian trumped five-times gold medalist Carolina Kostner to win the women's title on her debut appearance at the European championships in Budapest on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Public Help Sought in Southern California Serial Bank Robberies
headline.main: Public Help Sought in Southern California Serial Bank Robberies

docs.snippet: U.S. federal law enforcement on Friday sought the public's help in tracking down two serial bank robbers who have held up a combined 19 banks in Southern California in a little over a year, but who are not believed to be acting in concert....
